    h2 Value App Privacy Policy
    p Thanks for using Value! Here we describe how we collect, use and handle your information when you use our mobile application and services ("Services").

    h3 The information we collect
    p We collect information to provide better services to all of our users. From basic stuff like your personal information (Name, Email address, Nationality, Phone number etc.) we collected when you register or update your Value account, to more complex things like your trading behaviours and investment preferences. We also collect information when you use our services. We collect and use information in the following ways:
    ul
      li Location information
      p We may collect your actual location. We may use IP address, GPS and other possible technologies to determine location. For example, we use location information to recommend you investing and trading meetups nearby.
      li Device information
      p We collect device-specific information to help us provide better development plan. The information we collected such as your operating system version, hardware model and etc. will be used to provide more secure access to your account, and safeguard your information.
      li Local storage
      p We use local storage to store your account or application related information. This includes: your portfolios, watchlists, and transactions data etc., and application-specific information (such as quotes history, news and articles etc.) which we use caches or similar technologies.
      li Other information
      p We may also use mobile analytics (for example, Google Analytics)

    h3 Updating your personal information
    p We provide access to your personal information. We may ask you to verify your identity (by entering your password for example) when you update your information.

    h3 Changes
    p Our Privacy Policy may change from time to time. If we are involved in a reorganization, merger, acquisition, your information may be transferred as part of that deal. We will notify you via email of any such deal and post the most current version on the App and our website.

